name: look up
description:
my very first drop nft on hen

This photo is about my habit of looking up at the sky when I walk around the city.
It all started when I was little, my mother would often ask me to sit on the roof of our house to see the evening sky and the other kids playing kites. the funny thing about this memory is that when we see a plane passing we will shout "plane, please give us money"
